entry.title: Live Stream Conference: Island, Mainland, Coastland & Hinterland: Ceramic Perspectives on Connectivity in the Ancient Mediterranean
entry.content:
Island, Mainland, Coastland & Hinterland: Ceramic Perspectives on Connectivity in the Ancient Mediterranean
To access the livestream feed, please go to http://www.ustream.tv/channel/npapconnect directly or go to ustream.tv and search for "npapconnect".  Viewers can interact with the sessions via live social media streams on ustream.tv (see the website for details).
